@startuml
title C4 Container – US 2.2.2 Vessels

actor "Port Authority\nOfficer" as Officer

node "Client Layer" {
  [UI / API Client] as Client
}

node "Web API" {
  [VesselsController] as Ctl
}

node "Application Layer" {
  [VesselService] as Svc
}

database "Persistence" as Db
node "Domain" as Dom {
  [Vessel] as V
  [VesselType] as VT
  [Organization] as Org
  [ImoValidator] as IMO
}

Officer --> Client : register/update vessels
Client --> Ctl : POST/PUT/GET
Ctl --> Svc : CRUD operations
Svc --> Db : persist/retrieve
Svc ..> V : create/update
V --> VT : references type
V --> Org : references operator
V ..> IMO : validate IMO number

note right of V
  Vessel attributes:
  - IMO number (7-digit + check)
  - Name
  - Vessel Type
  - Operator/Owner Org
  - Actual dimensions ≤ type max
end note

@enduml
